  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK334">
<l>nāḷeṉa voṉṟupōṟ kāṭṭi yuyirīrum</l>
<l>vāḷa tuṇarvārp peṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Time, which shows itself (to the ignorant) as if it were something (real) is in the estimation of the wise (only) a saw which cuts down life.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
